## Installation

You can install the development version of `{cd2030.extractor}` like so:

```{r, eval = FALSE}
devtools::install_github('aphrcwaro/dhis2')
```

## Run

You can launch the application by running:

```{r, eval = FALSE}
cd2030.extractor::run_app()
```
